    "description": "The orthophoto mosaic SWISSIMAGE HIST 1946 is a composition of historical black and white aerial photographs from 1946 («US flight mission») over the whole of Switzerland with a ground resolution of 1 m. An orthophoto is an aerial image in which the distortions created by the camera and the relief are corrected.",
